```python
### maxSumOfThreeSubarrays 
from typing import *
def f_gold(nums: List[int], k: int) -> List[int]:   # --- py stmt 1
    s = s1 = s2 = s3 = 0   # --- py stmt 2
    mx1 = mx12 = 0   # --- py stmt 3
    idx1, idx12 = 0, ()   # --- py stmt 4
    ans = []   # --- py stmt 5
    for i in range(k * 2, len(nums)):   # --- py stmt 6
        s1 += nums[i - k * 2]   # --- py stmt 7
        s2 += nums[i - k]   # --- py stmt 8
        s3 += nums[i]   # --- py stmt 9
        if i >= k * 3 - 1:   # --- py stmt 10
            if s1 > mx1:   # --- py stmt 11
                mx1 = s1   # --- py stmt 12
                idx1 = i - k * 3 + 1   # --- py stmt 13
            if mx1 + s2 > mx12:   # --- py stmt 14
                mx12 = mx1 + s2   # --- py stmt 15
                idx12 = (idx1, i - k * 2 + 1)   # --- py stmt 16
            if mx12 + s3 > s:   # --- py stmt 17
                s = mx12 + s3   # --- py stmt 18
                ans = [*idx12, i - k + 1]   # --- py stmt 19
            s1 -= nums[i - k * 3 + 1]   # --- py stmt 20
            s2 -= nums[i - k * 2 + 1]   # --- py stmt 21
            s3 -= nums[i - k + 1]   # --- py stmt 22
    return ans   # --- py stmt 23
```
